N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 23.6 - Ineligibility for other benefits

State Regulations

Any not-for-profit organization receiving a loan from the
fund shall be ineligible to receive interest from a State agency, notwithstanding the provisions of section
179-v
of
the State Finance Law and shall be ineligible to receive advance payments, notwithstanding section
179-u
of
the State Finance Law. Notes
